Text:
Thank you!  Great upload.  Quality is OK, most of the tracks are 128 or 160kbps, about 12-15 are 190kbps+

Torrent is missing a few tracks on volume 3, but if you look in the torrent description on this page he's accurately advertised what he offers.

314159m83, is there any way you can compile this again with higher quality and/or the missing tracks?  If not, thanks anyway, you did a good job on this one.
